      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and ultimate tensile strength were measured from Ti-6Al-4V coupons from the same production lot as the tested screws. Screw geometry was characterized by CMM with tolerances propagated into the UQ analysis. Coefficient of friction was measured by pin-on-flat testing. Input uncertainty bounds established at 95% confidence. Gradation 3 achieved."
