      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled and tested: six at Laboratory A (FDA/CDRH) and five at Laboratory B (DePuy Synthes). All constructs were inspected by CMM prior to testing and confirmed within design tolerances. Inter-laboratory variability characterized. Gradation 3 achieved."
