      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions match COU loading environment; multiple load levels or configurations tested to characterize model behavior across the operating range.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under ASTM F1717 standard conditions (compression-bending at 5° offset, displacement-controlled at 5 mm/min). However, only a single test configuration was evaluated; no variation in rod diameter, screw angulation, or inter-body distance was included. This limits confidence that the model captures behavior across the full COU envelope. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3 — noted as below-threshold factor."
    },
    {
