      "rationale": "FEA model geometry was constructed from CMM measurements of the physical test constructs. Material properties were assigned from lot-specific coupon data used in the same test campaign. Boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture kinematics. Residual deviations (surface finish, assembly torque) were assessed by sensitivity analysis; impact on QoIs bounded at <1.5%. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
