      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria: percent differences of 4.2%, 6.8%, and 7.3% respectively, and E/uval values of 0.87, 1.41, and 1.58 respectively, all below 1.96. Force-displacement curve overlay shows consistent shape agreement through the elastic, yield, and post-yield regimes. Gradation 3 achieved."
