      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and required by FDA for 510(k) submissions for posterior thoracolumbar fixation systems. These QoIs directly correspond to the mechanical performance parameters relevant to clinical use. Gradation 3 achieved."
